Sonae Plans to Increase Investment in 2011, CEO Tells Economico

-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 
2011-03-17T08:31:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/sonae-plans-to-increase-investment-in-2011-ceo-tells-economico.html
  Sonae (SON)  SGPS SA, a holding company
that controls Portuguese retailer Continente, expects to
increase investment in 2011, Chief Executive Officer Paulo
Azevedo said in an interview with Diario Economico.  The company aims to increase its market share this year,
the Portuguese newspaper said. 2011 will be “a very tough
year,” Azevedo said, according to Diario.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
